---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于我们 | Geppetto - AI驱动的精密制造革命" description="了解Geppetto团队，我们是AI+学徒制造模式的开创者，致力于用人工智能技术重新定义精密制造行业，为客户提供更快、更准、更省的制造解决方案。">
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-600 via-blue-600 to-purple-800 text-white py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
                🚀 重新定义精密制造
              </h1>
              <p class="text-2xl text-blue-100 mb-8">
                我们是Geppetto，一家专注于AI+学徒制造模式的科技公司。我们相信，人工智能与传统工艺的完美结合，将开启制造业的全新时代。
              </p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">2021</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">公司成立</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">50+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">合作客户</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">500+</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">成功项目</div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
                  <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">99.5%</div>
                  <div class="text-sm text-blue-200">质量合格率</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="relative">
              <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl p-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">🎯 我们的使命</h3>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                  <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-300 rounded-full"></div>
                    <span class="text-lg">让AI技术普惠每一个制造企业</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-300 rounded-full"></div>
                    <span class="text-lg">用创新降低精密制造门槛</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-yellow-300 rounded-full"></div>
                    <span class="text-lg">重塑全球制造业竞争格局</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 公司故事 -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
              📖 我们的故事
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
              从一个大胆的想法到行业变革的引领者
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative">
            <!-- 时间线 -->
            <div class="absolute left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
            
            <div class="space-y-16">
              <!-- 2021年 - 创立 -->
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1/2 pr-8">
                  <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 ml-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">🌱 创立初心</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      三位来自清华、MIT和斯坦福的工程师发现，传统制造业面临着"技能传承断层"的危机。资深师傅即将退休，年轻学徒缺乏实战经验，优质制造能力正在流失。
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      我们决定用AI技术来"数字化"师傅的经验和智慧，让机器学习替代漫长的学徒培养过程，同时保留人类工匠的精神和判断力。
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2021</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/2 pl-8"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- 2022年 - 技术突破 -->
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1/2 pr-8"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2022</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/2 pl-8">
                  <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mr-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">🧠 AI+学徒模式诞生</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      经过一年的技术攻关，我们成功开发出第一代AI制造系统。它能够在3秒内分析CAD图纸，生成最优加工路径，并实时指导学徒进行精密操作。
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      首个客户项目取得成功：机器人关节件精度从±0.05mm提升到±0.015mm，成本降低35%，交付时间从14天缩短到24小时。
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- 2023年 - 快速发展 -->
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1/2 pr-8">
                  <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-8 ml-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">📈 规模化验证</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      我们的模式开始在多个行业得到验证：航空航天、医疗器械、精密仪器。客户从初创公司扩展到世界500强企业。
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      成功案例包括：为中国商飞制造复杂曲面结构件，为医疗器械公司生产FDA认证的钛合金组件，为机器人公司提供极速原型制造服务。
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2023</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/2 pl-8"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- 2024年 - 行业引领 -->
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1/2 pr-8"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center relative z-10">
                  <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2024</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-1/2 pl-8">
                  <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-2xl p-8 mr-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">🏆 行业变革引领者</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                      我们的AI+学徒制造模式被誉为"制造业的ChatGPT时刻"。多家知名投资机构完成A轮融资，估值突破10亿元。
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                      目前服务客户覆盖15个国家，累计完成项目500+个，节省客户成本超过2000万元，获得多项国际制造业创新奖项。
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 核心价值观 -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
              🎯 核心价值观
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
              指引我们前进方向的核心理念
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🚀</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">创新驱动</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                我们相信技术创新是推动行业进步的唯一动力。每一个AI算法的优化，都可能改变一个制造企业的命运。
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🎯</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">精益求精</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                从±0.1mm到±0.008mm，每一个精度的提升都代表着我们对完美的追求。质量是我们的生命线。
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🤝</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">客户至上</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                客户的成功就是我们的成功。我们不仅提供制造服务，更是客户业务增长的合作伙伴。
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🌱</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">持续学习</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                我们的AI系统每天都在学习和进化，团队也在不断学习新技术、新理念，保持行业领先地位。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 团队介绍 -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
              👥 核心团队
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
              来自全球顶尖院校和公司的精英团队
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <!-- 创始人&CEO -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors duration-300">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-white text-3xl font-bold">李</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">李博士</h3>
              <p class="text-purple-600 font-semibold mb-4">创始人 & CEO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                清华大学机械工程博士，MIT访问学者。前特斯拉高级工程师，在智能制造领域有10年经验。
              </p>
              <div class="flex justify-center space-x-2">
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">AI算法</span>
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">制造工艺</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTO -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:bg-green-50 transition-colors duration-300">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-white text-3xl font-bold">王</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">王工程师</h3>
              <p class="text-green-600 font-semibold mb-4">联合创始人 & CTO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                斯坦福大学计算机科学硕士，前Google AI研究科学家。专注于机器学习在工业领域的应用。
              </p>
              <div class="flex justify-center space-x-2">
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">深度学习</span>
                <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">计算机视觉</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- COO -->
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:bg-yellow-50 transition-colors duration-300">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="text-white text-3xl font-bold">张</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">张总</h3>
              <p class="text-yellow-600 font-semibold mb-4">联合创始人 & COO</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                北京理工大学MBA，前华为供应链总监。在制造业运营管理和质量控制方面有15年经验。
              </p>
              <div class="flex justify-center space-x-2">
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">运营管理</span>
                <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">质量控制</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 团队数据 -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 to-blue-100 rounded-3xl p-12">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">🏢 团队构成</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">50+</div>
                <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">团队成员</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">来自20+顶尖院校</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">15+</div>
                <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">AI工程师</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">平均5年AI经验</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">20+</div>
                <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">制造专家</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">平均10年工艺经验</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-yellow-600 mb-2">80%</div>
                <div class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700">硕博比例</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">持续技术创新</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 技术实力 -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
              🔬 技术实力
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
              领先的AI技术与深厚的制造工艺完美结合
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <!-- AI技术栈 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center">
                🤖 AI技术栈
              </h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">深度学习框架</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">TensorFlow</span>
                    <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">PyTorch</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">计算机视觉</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">OpenCV</span>
                    <span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">YOLO</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">优化算法</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">遗传算法</span>
                    <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">强化学习</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">云计算平台</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <span class="bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">阿里云</span>
                    <span class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">AWS</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 制造能力 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 flex items-center">
                🏭 制造能力
              </h3>
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">加工精度</span>
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold">±0.008mm</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">材料种类</span>
                  <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold">50+ 种</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">加工方式</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">CNC</span>
                    <span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">3D打印</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-700">质量认证</span>
                  <div class="flex space-x-2">
                    <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">ISO 9001</span>
                    <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">AS9100D</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 办公环境 -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">
              🏢 工作环境
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
              现代化的研发中心和生产基地
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-4xl text-center mb-4">🏗️</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 text-center">AI研发中心</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
                位于北京中关村的3000平米研发中心，配备最先进的GPU集群和算法实验室
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-4xl text-center mb-4">🏭</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 text-center">智能工厂</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
                苏州工业园区的5000平米智能工厂，集成了20台高精度CNC设备和自动化产线
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
              <div class="text-4xl text-center mb-4">🔬</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3 text-center">质检中心</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-center">
                配备三坐标测量机、激光干涉仪等高精度检测设备，确保每个产品质量
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 技术创新与行业影响 -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
